// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0607 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: df5ff6b2-5978-5eae-addd-3087dac54fc5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
